<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NBA Champions 2024-2025</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><%=name%> are your 2024-2025 NBA Champions!</h1>
        <p>Congratulations to <%= name %> on their victory!</p>
        </div>
</body>
</html>